data.description: JUST REDUCED 20K.........Welcome to this gorgeous neighborhood! Opportunity Abounds with Impressive Home featuring A Sparkling Kitchen Equipped with Ample Cabinets and Generous Counter Space/Breakfast Nook. Flow into the Formal Dining Room perfect for Candlelit Dinners.  Large Master Bedroom & Nice Spacious 2nd & 3rd bedrooms! Step outside to a Great 2 tiered Deck Perfect for Grilling, Overlooking a Gorgeous Fenced (see Agent Remarks) in Backyard with Wired Storage Building!  Partially finished Basement featuring Huge Den with a Cozy Fireplace, Gas Logs and Wet Bar leading out to a Fabulous Patio. New SS Appliances to Remain, New Interior Paint and New Vinyl Plank Flooring! Updated Full Baths! 2 Car Basement Garage, 1 Car Detached Carport, Extra Driveway to Storage Building, NO HOA - All on a Corner Lot just waiting for you!
